<a href="/wiki/File:CDW_ring.png" class="image" title="Image:CDW ring.png"><img alt="Image:CDW ring.png" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/5/52/CDW_ring.png" width="11" height="20" border="0" /></a><a href="/wiki/File:CDW_3b.png" class="image" title="Image:CDW 3b.png"><img alt="Image:CDW 3b.png" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/2/24/CDW_3b.png" width="6" height="20" border="0" /></a><a href="/wiki/File:CDW_dot.png" class="image" title="Image:CDW dot.png"><img alt="Image:CDW dot.png" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/f/fc/CDW_dot.png" width="7" height="20" border="0" /></a><a href="/wiki/File:CDW_3b.png" class="image" title="Image:CDW 3b.png"><img alt="Image:CDW 3b.png" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/2/24/CDW_3b.png" width="6" height="20" border="0" /></a><a href="/wiki/File:CDW_dot.png" class="image" title="Image:CDW dot.png"><img alt="Image:CDW dot.png" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/f/fc/CDW_dot.png" width="7" height="20" border="0" /></a><a href="/wiki/File:CDW_3b.png" class="image" title="Image:CDW 3b.png"><img alt="Image:CDW 3b.png" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/2/24/CDW_3b.png" width="6" height="20" border="0" /></a><a href="/wiki/File:CDW_dot.png" class="image" title="Image:CDW dot.png"><img alt="Image:CDW dot.png" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/f/fc/CDW_dot.png" width="7" height="20" border="0" /></a><a href="/wiki/File:CDW_3b.png" class="image" title="Image:CDW 3b.png"><img alt="Image:CDW 3b.png" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/2/24/CDW_3b.png" width="6" height="20" border="0" /></a><a href="/wiki/File:CDW_dot.png" class="image" title="Image:CDW dot.png"><img alt="Image:CDW dot.png" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/f/fc/CDW_dot.png" width="7" height="20" border="0" /></a><a href="/wiki/File:CDW_3b.png" class="image" title="Image:CDW 3b.png"><img alt="Image:CDW 3b.png" src="http://upload.wik